The paper deals with privacy-preserving mechanisms and their guarantees, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the capacity of memory-less channels, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of quantization operators to ensure noiseless privacy is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the privacy merits of noiseless privacy using multiple datasets, which is a topic in data science (cs.DS) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
